                <mxCell id="notes1" value="&lt;b&gt;How to use this canvas&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Each card is one host screen&lt;br&gt;2. No lines between cards on purpose&lt;br&gt;3. Add new screens nearby when flow expands&lt;br&gt;4. Use the .km file for logic tree&lt;br&gt;5. Use this file for visual screen boards" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#111111;fontSize=15;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
